  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Adult patients requiring surgery for esotropia will be randomized to surgery under topical
      anesthesia or sub-Tenon's anesthesia. Amount of surgery required with the two anesthetic
      procedures will be compared. Motor and sensory outcome of the two treatment groups will also
      be compared.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
