  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Esotropia deviation angle equal to or lower than 45 prism dioptres (requiring one or
             two-muscle surgery)

          -  Visual acuity at least 20/40 in each eye

          -  Cooperation for topical anesthesia

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Paretic or restrictive strabismus

          -  Previous eye muscle surgery

          -  Significant eye disease other than strabismus
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
